    "description": "&quot;Bunker 21: A tale of solitude and survival&quot; is a story-driven first-person action game that transports you into a post-apocalyptic world where humanity has vanished. You play as Andrei, the sole survivor, who is searching for answers and hope in a devastated world.<br><br>Andrei's journey leads him to Bunker 21, a place filled with secrets and dangers. Here, he encounters monstrous creatures and unravels the bunker's mysteries.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Immerse yourself in the Apocalypse</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082510/extras/378a1af847318928fbc50d00e56fe5a2.poster.avif?t=1770750347\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082510/extras/378a1af847318928fbc50d00e56fe5a2.webm?t=1770750347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082510/extras/378a1af847318928fbc50d00e56fe5a2.mp4?t=1770750347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The world you once knew has disappeared. The cause of this apocalypse remains a mystery, but as you navigate through the remnants of a shattered civilization, you piece together fragments of the past and slowly uncover the truth.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle mutants and bosses</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082510/extras/ea6baeb9739a71d24b452567bbcc4c46.poster.avif?t=1770750347\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082510/extras/ea6baeb9739a71d24b452567bbcc4c46.webm?t=1770750347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082510/extras/ea6baeb9739a71d24b452567bbcc4c46.mp4?t=1770750347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In the silence of the world, danger lurks around every corner. You encounter aggressive mutants, humans transformed due to secret experiments. Armed with a variety of weapons, including firearms and melee weapons, you engage in a fight for survival.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Venture into unknown worlds</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082510/extras/170a31b4b0067d8d578097861b44024c.poster.avif?t=1770750347\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082510/extras/170a31b4b0067d8d578097861b44024c.webm?t=1770750347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082510/extras/170a31b4b0067d8d578097861b44024c.mp4?t=1770750347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Prepare yourself for a journey beyond reality. New worlds, alternate dimensions, the unknown awaits you. Beyond the portal, new challenges and discoveries await.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082510/extras/e8863d82534aa7643f55548c29dffa5d.poster.avif?t=1770750347\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082510/extras/e8863d82534aa7643f55548c29dffa5d.webm?t=1770750347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082510/extras/e8863d82534aa7643f55548c29dffa5d.mp4?t=1770750347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Immerse yourself in a story filled with characters and puzzles. Navigate through six chapters, each testing your will to survive.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve puzzles and uncover secrets</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082510/extras/e48623022c667020b2cc249323ba12b8.poster.avif?t=1770750347\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082510/extras/e48623022c667020b2cc249323ba12b8.webm?t=1770750347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082510/extras/e48623022c667020b2cc249323ba12b8.mp4?t=1770750347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Engage in puzzles, gather resources, and uncover notes that shed light on this world.<br><br>&quot;Bunker 21: A tale of solitude and survival&quot; offers diverse gameplay and a narrative that pulls you into the game.<br><br>Welcome to a world of mysteries, dangers, and hope. Welcome to Bunker 21.",
